abstract: Bold 'N Determined won it all with a name that told it all at Belmont Park yesterday. "A gustsy filly" is the way her jockey described her bold and determined ride to a head victory in the $140,000 Coaching Club American Oaks.

abstract: SEA GIRT, N.J., June 27--Marching, saluting, sitting, and accepting their uniform badges with military bearing and precision, the 30 women in the first all-female class of New Jersey state troopers graduated today in sundrenched ceremonies at their seaside training camp here.
headline_main: Jersey Graduates Its All-Female State Police Class; 'It's Like the Elite'
